name: APPLEPYE
description: APPLEPYE is an essential component of PYESwap's reward system for Farms and Pools. APPLEPYE can be earned from Staking Pools and Farms, can be won it in the lottery, or purchased. APPLEPYE can be staked to earn PEACHPYE, used to place a bet on Coinflip and used to mint NFTs on the PYESWAP NFT Marketplace.
